---
title: Country Gravy Pork Chops with a Potato and Collard Green Hash
description: Pork chops and gravy is a timeless, simple, and classic combination—how can you go wrong with tender lean meat smothered in a rich and creamy pan sauce? Adding potatoes and collard greens only makes it better. The spuds bring plenty of crispy roasted comfort, while the veg adds heartiness (and lots of vitamin A and C).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/country-gravy-pork-chops-dc580d10.jpg
